OL,3,CUkraine enters fifth year of war with
OL,4,Ccivilians increasingly baring the brunt
OL,6,FAnd so begins Ukraine's fifth year of
OL,7,Fwar.
OL,9,FTime may have dimmed the spectacle of
OL,10,Fbattle, but it has not diminished the
OL,11,Fbrutality.
OL,13,FThe frontline shifts backwards and
OL,14,Fforward at a glacial pace, but it is
OL,15,Fthe civilian frontline which is
OL,16,Ffeeling the dreadful impact now.
OL,18,FThe last year was the deadliest so far
OL,19,Ffor civilians, up 31% on the year
OL,20,Fbefore and 70% up on 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
