OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1771956278
OL,3,CUkraine enters fifth year of war with
OL,4,Ccivilians increasingly baring the brunt
OL,6,FAccording to the UN, more than 2,000
OL,7,Fcivilians died last year, and more
OL,8,Fthan 12,000 were injured.
OL,10,FEvery one of those numbers is enough
OL,11,Fto destroy multiple lives, and don't
OL,12,Fforget, many families are also
OL,13,Fmourning the deaths of those civilians
OL,14,Fwho signed up and died in service.
OL,16,FDrones are responsible for many of
OL,17,Fthose deaths as towns and cities are
OL,18,Froutinely targeted. Home, however far
OL,19,Ffrom the front, is no longer a place
OL,20,Fof safety and generations of
OL,21,FUkrainians are having to adapt to that.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
