CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1771956278
OL,3,CUkraine enters fifth year of war with
OL,4,Ccivilians increasingly baring the brunt
OL,6,FThe continual winter attacks on the
OL,7,Fpower network continue to take heat
OL,8,Fand hope.
OL,10,FLittle wonder there is a war weariness
OL,11,Falongside resilience.
OL,13,FThis is now an attritional conflict
OL,14,Fmeasured less in territorial
OL,15,Fbreakthroughs and more in endurance -
OL,16,Fof soldiers, civilians, and
OL,17,Fpoliticians at home and abroad.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
