PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1771956278
OL,3,CUkraine enters fifth year of war with
OL,4,Ccivilians increasingly baring the brunt
OL,6,FWars of attrition are fought as much
OL,7,Fin budgets and parliaments as on
OL,8,Fbattlefields.
OL,10,FFour years on, the Ukraine war is no
OL,11,Flonger a short-term crisis.
OL,13,FIt is a defining, unresolved feature
OL,14,Fof the current geopolitical order `
OL,15,Fand one that will shape European
OL,16,Fsecurity for years to come.
